I think this is the first time I have posted an at home workout from my guides @veganaestheticscommunity ! The home workouts tend to be in circuit form since the weight is low so we increase intensity through time! This is one of two circuits in the workout. Each circuit is made up of 5 exercises that you perform back to back for 30 seconds each with no rest in between OR with 30 seconds rest between exercises if you are a total beginner. Repeat this circuit 3-5 times:
.
1. Dumbbell single leg glute bridge (30 seconds)
2. Dumbbell RDL (30 seconds)
3. Dumbbell squat to press (30 seconds)
4. Dumbbell overhead lunges (30 seconds)
5. Jump squats (30 seconds)
.
